1
00:01:23,440 --> 00:01:24,700
You admitted your past

2
00:01:24,880 --> 00:01:26,680
with Lu Jingxi to the reporters.

3
00:01:27,240 --> 00:01:30,240
Aren't you afraid of making the public opinion worse?

4
00:01:30,440 --> 00:01:32,960
I'm burning my bridges.

5
00:01:33,360 --> 00:01:35,880
They won't have any leverage over me anymore.

6
00:01:35,880 --> 00:01:37,160
Even if it's brought up,

7
00:01:37,160 --> 00:01:39,360
it's just a thing of the past.

8
00:01:39,600 --> 00:01:42,720
It's better than cheating during marriage, right?

9
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,610
You thought it through.

10
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:47,700
Since that's the case,

11
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:49,600
from now on in the Lu family,

12
00:01:49,600 --> 00:01:51,080
just ignore Lu Jingxi.

13
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:53,080
If he dares to harass you,

14
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:54,840
tell me immediately.

15
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:58,759
Mr. Lu doesn't trust me.

16
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:01,960
I'm just cooperating with the PR plan.

17
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:04,880
We need to keep up the loving couple persona.

18
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:08,490
That's how we can turn the public opinion around.

19
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:10,520
Loving couple persona?

20
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:12,720
How loving?

21
00:02:21,760 --> 00:02:23,079
How loving do you want?

22
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:31,320
It's getting late.

23
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:34,720
Mr. Lu, go back to your room and sleep.

24
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,120
Get some rest.

25
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:46,920
Jingheng.

26
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:48,850
What are you doing here?

27
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,560
I was just passing by.

28
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:51,880
Get some rest.

29
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:53,320
Cousin.

30
00:02:53,640 --> 00:02:55,200
Still awake this late?

31
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:57,370
Your brother and I are going to bed.

32
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,720
Do you want to come in?

33
00:02:59,440 --> 00:03:00,520
It's nothing.

34
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:01,400
I'm leaving.

35
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:12,040
What kind of spell did Shen Zhixia

36
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:14,800
cast on Jingheng?

37
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:17,560
He was determined not to sleep with her,

38
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:19,720
but now he defends her at every turn.

39
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:25,260
What are you doing?

40
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:27,579
Su Yuran is at the door.

41
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:29,250
Let's mess with her.

42
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:34,320
Then put your hands on my shoulders.

43
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,800
I don't need you to teach me.

44
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,120
I know how.

45
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,840
She finally left.

46
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,840
The show is over.

47
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,820
Why are you panicking?

48
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:13,700
I'm not panicking.

49
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,560
You...

50
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,959
We must put on a full show.

51
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:22,680
If the fact that we sleep in separate rooms

52
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:24,410
is discovered by others again,

53
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:27,040
more rumors will probably spread.

54
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:30,560
Why don't we

55
00:04:33,400 --> 00:04:34,659
sleep in the same room?

56
00:04:35,159 --> 00:04:36,960
I don't think that's a good idea.

57
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,920
Why not?

58
00:04:58,880 --> 00:05:00,720
Don't worry. We'll sleep separately.

59
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:02,050
I'll sleep on the floor.

60
00:05:05,320 --> 00:05:07,120
You should have said so earlier.

61
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:17,160
Is the matter resolved perfectly this time?

62
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,240
I saw many people online

63
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,960
saying they support the Young Madam.

64
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:20,880
Exactly.

65
00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:22,930
Good morning, Young Madam.

66
00:05:23,080 --> 00:05:24,440
Good morning, Young Madam.

67
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:25,960
Go eat breakfast. Stop working.

68
00:05:25,960 --> 00:05:26,600
Yes.

69
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,600
Young Master.

70
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:34,860
You seem to be in a good mood, Sister-in-law.

71
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:38,120
I didn't expect you to show off at the press conference.

72
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:40,380
What makes you so proud, sister-in-law?

73
00:05:40,960 --> 00:05:42,120
It seems that slap

74
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:44,520
didn't teach you a lesson, Second Young Master.

75
00:05:44,520 --> 00:05:45,320
Or is it that

76
00:05:45,960 --> 00:05:49,020
you naturally enjoy getting hit, Second Young Master?

77
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:51,600
Even the wind from sister-in-law's slap

78
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:53,320
smells sweet.

79
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:56,600
Honey.

80
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:03,340
Don't catch a cold.

81
00:06:11,840 --> 00:06:12,760
You have a weak stomach.

82
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:14,960
Don't drink coffee on an empty stomach.

83
00:06:19,880 --> 00:06:21,140
Cooperate with the PR.

84
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:24,920
Thank you, Hubby.

85
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,490
You're welcome.

86
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:38,860
Second Master,

87
00:06:39,080 --> 00:06:40,400
Eldest Master, Young Madam,

88
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:41,600
the Master is waiting for you in the living room.

89
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:42,930
He wants you to go there.

90
00:06:51,960 --> 00:06:54,290
Thanks to the Wen family's help this time,

91
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:57,400
the public opinion was suppressed so quickly.

92
00:06:59,000 --> 00:06:59,840
Shen Zhixia,

93
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:03,400
don't think that just because the incident is over,

94
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:06,200
you can do whatever you want in the Lu family again.

95
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:07,480
That's right.

96
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,720
Zhixia was still too impulsive

97
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:11,840
to directly admit her past with my cousin

98
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:13,440
at the press conference this time.

99
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:15,770
If the public opinion wasn't stabilized,

100
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:18,360
it would be very difficult to remedy it later.

101
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,960
Thank you for the reminder, cousin.

102
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:22,480
But speaking of the press conference,

103
00:07:23,080 --> 00:07:24,600
a reporter asked me that day

104
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:27,130
why I let a maid of the Lu family take the blame.

105
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:29,240
How did others know?

106
00:07:29,280 --> 00:07:31,000
Or did someone give her a script

107
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:32,330
and let her read from it?

108
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:34,080
You're overthinking it.

109
00:07:34,080 --> 00:07:35,440
Don't be in a hurry to explain.

110
00:07:35,440 --> 00:07:36,700
I didn't say it was you.

111
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:43,600
Honey.

112
00:07:43,960 --> 00:07:45,480
How's the investigation

113
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,600
going?

114
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:53,720
Dad, please take a look yourself.

115
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:59,610
I found out that Su Yuran contacted reporters

116
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:00,840
to smear Zhixia,

117
00:08:01,440 --> 00:08:04,700
and even let these two reporters into the press conference

118
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:06,080
to intentionally make things difficult for Zhixia

119
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:08,000
and ruin the Lu family's reputation.

120
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:08,720
Miss Shen,

121
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:10,120
you were dating Lu Jingxi before your marriage,

122
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,080
but now you've married his brother.

123
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:12,280
Is this a fraud?

124
00:08:12,280 --> 00:08:13,760
You know you have a dark history,

125
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:15,120
yet you still married into the Lu family.

126
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:16,240
Did you intentionally bring this stain

127
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:17,280
to drag down the Lu family's reputation?

128
00:08:17,280 --> 00:08:18,880
Don't you feel any guilt at all?

129
00:08:18,880 --> 00:08:19,800
I didn't expect

130
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:22,720
a person who harms the Lu family's interests like this.

131
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:24,250
Keep it in the Lu residence.

132
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,440
Su Yuran.

133
00:08:40,159 --> 00:08:42,490
The Lu family has treated you well, right?

134
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:45,320
Your parents passed away early.

135
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:47,880
I was the one who asked Manyun to bring you to the Lu family.

136
00:08:47,880 --> 00:08:50,800
We never mistreated you in terms of food and clothing.

137
00:08:50,800 --> 00:08:52,160
You wanted to start a business,

138
00:08:52,160 --> 00:08:53,960
and the Lu family invested in it.

139
00:08:54,520 --> 00:08:56,450
Is this how you repay the Lu family?

140
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,600
It's not like that, Uncle.

141
00:08:58,760 --> 00:09:00,000
Uncle, listen to me.

142
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:00,600
I... I...

143
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:02,280
Leaking dirt to reporters,

144
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:05,200
sneaking people into the press conference.

145
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:06,200
All these things,

146
00:09:06,560 --> 00:09:09,080
which of them wasn't done on purpose?

147
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:11,840
What are you scheming?

148
00:09:11,880 --> 00:09:13,880
Did you think I was too old to notice?

149
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,800
Let me tell you,

150
00:09:16,520 --> 00:09:18,280
even if Jingheng were to remarry,

151
00:09:18,280 --> 00:09:19,520
it would never be you.

152
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:24,170
The reputation of our Lu family

153
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:27,000
cannot be ruined by an outsider.

154
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:29,480
Over the years,

155
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:32,080
the money you borrowed from the Lu family,

156
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,810
must be paid back within a week.

157
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:35,360
And

158
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:37,280
starting today,

159
00:09:37,760 --> 00:09:39,090
without my permission,

160
00:09:39,880 --> 00:09:42,810
she is not allowed to step into the Lu family's house.

161
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:43,920
Aunt.

162
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:45,560
You know about this.

163
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:46,560
I simply don't...

164
00:09:46,560 --> 00:09:47,640
You bastard!

165
00:09:47,800 --> 00:09:48,640
Someone come!

166
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:50,000
Throw her out!

167
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:50,560
Yes.

168
00:09:50,560 --> 00:09:51,600
Aunt, about this,

169
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:53,240
I really don't have the ability

170
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:55,320
to repay the money now, Aunt.

171
00:09:56,880 --> 00:09:58,000
Aunt!

172
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,640
Aunt!

173
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:03,360
Aunt!

174
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:12,080
Let go of me!

175
00:10:12,680 --> 00:10:13,720
Let me go.

176
00:10:14,160 --> 00:10:15,320
Let me go.

177
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,240
Shen Zhixia.

178
00:10:30,160 --> 00:10:31,680
I will remember this.

179
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:34,880
I will make you pay double.

180
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:39,000
Last time I asked you to accompany me,

181
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,280
your dress got dirty.

182
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:44,440
Consider this bracelet an apology.

183
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:45,810
Thank you for your help.

184
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:47,970
You are too polite, Mr. Wen.

185
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:50,320
But I'm curious.

186
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:53,740
Why did you need me to pretend to be your girlfriend?

187
00:10:53,800 --> 00:10:55,080
With your conditions,

188
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:57,810
it shouldn't be hard to find a girlfriend.

189
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,720
My family is pushing me hard.

190
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:02,980
I had to put on an act in front of my cousin.

191
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:06,090
If I were to really be your girlfriend,

192
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:08,000
it wouldn't be out of the question.

193
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:10,120
Think about it, Mr. Wen.

194
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:11,800
Thanks.

195
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:19,640
Miss Wen.

196
00:11:22,680 --> 00:11:23,480
Shuyi,

197
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:25,760
why didn't you tell me in advance

198
00:11:25,760 --> 00:11:27,820
when you came to eat at my restaurant?

199
00:11:28,520 --> 00:11:29,720
You were busy with your girlfriend.

200
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:30,980
How could I bother you?

201
00:11:32,280 --> 00:11:34,720
She has something to do today and has to leave early.

202
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:37,000
I'll invite you guys to go horseback riding another day.

203
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:39,120
She might be your future sister-in-law.

204
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,640
It's good for you to get to know each other.

205
00:11:40,640 --> 00:11:41,640
I don't have time.

206
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:44,680
I've been busy with Jingheng recently.

207
00:11:44,680 --> 00:11:45,480
I'm a bit busy.

208
00:11:47,400 --> 00:11:50,000
I want to invite Jingheng for a meal later.

209
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:51,900
Book a private room for me,

210
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:53,640
just for the two of us.

211
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:56,640
Make it romantic.

212
00:11:56,800 --> 00:11:57,920
I told you

213
00:11:58,680 --> 00:12:00,160
to stay away from Jingheng.

214
00:12:00,160 --> 00:12:01,420
He's already married.

215
00:12:03,640 --> 00:12:06,120
Are you worried I'll ruin his family,

216
00:12:06,800 --> 00:12:09,320
or that I'll actually steal him away?

217
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:12,320
If I have a meal alone with Jingheng,

218
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,640
would you be unhappy?

219
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:18,580
I'm worried you'll regret making a mistake.

220
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:20,480
Regret?

221
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:24,200
I've never regretted

222
00:12:24,560 --> 00:12:25,880
anything I've done.

223
00:12:28,160 --> 00:12:29,000
Besides,

224
00:12:29,920 --> 00:12:31,560
what could happen if I have a meal alone

225
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:32,480
with Jingheng?

226
00:12:33,560 --> 00:12:34,720
If you're worried,

227
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:36,220
then accompany me.

228
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:39,480
But you probably don't have time.

229
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:41,340
You just saw your girlfriend off,

230
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:43,200
maybe you have other things to do.

231
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,240
I'll eat with you.

232
00:12:44,880 --> 00:12:46,240
Don't go looking for Jingheng.

233
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:47,040
Waiter.

234
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:54,130
She doesn't eat spicy food.

235
00:12:55,040 --> 00:12:55,840
This,

236
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:57,640
this,

237
00:12:59,640 --> 00:13:00,440
this,

238
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:02,240
and this.

239
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:05,120
Make sure none of them are spicy.

240
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:06,440
And this one.

241
00:13:07,800 --> 00:13:09,440
How come you have time to take me out today?

242
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,680
Aren't you busy?

243
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:12,920
You looked unhappy at home.

244
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:14,920
What is this?

245
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:16,720
A reward for playing the loving couple with you,

246
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:17,320
or a prize for helping you

247
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:19,450
drive away someone from the Su family?

248
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:21,120
Think whatever you want.

249
00:13:21,640 --> 00:13:22,720
Then it's your treat today.

250
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:24,120
Isn't that young Mrs. Lu?

251
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:25,770
She had a scandal recently.

252
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:27,240
She looks elegant.

253
00:13:27,240 --> 00:13:29,240
I didn't expect that to happen before the wedding.

254
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:29,880
Yeah.

255
00:13:29,880 --> 00:13:30,680
I'll take you to

256
00:13:30,680 --> 00:13:32,140
a more interesting place.

257
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:33,200
Let's go.

258
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:34,520
It really is them.

259
00:14:44,280 --> 00:14:46,240
Shen Zhixia, Lu Jingheng,

260
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:49,240
why do you get to be so happy?

261
00:15:06,720 --> 00:15:06,980
Cast

262
00:15:07,400 --> 00:15:08,040
Lu Jingheng: Deng Chaoyuan

263
00:15:08,040 --> 00:15:09,040
Lu Jingxi: Liu Yufeng

264
00:15:09,040 --> 00:15:09,320
Su Manyun: Ge Wenxi

265
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:09,640
Wen Zhuocheng: Wang Ye

266
00:15:09,640 --> 00:15:09,920
Su Yuran: Ma Jie

267
00:15:09,920 --> 00:15:10,600
Su Yuran: Ma Jie

268
00:15:10,600 --> 00:15:11,280
Shen Jingyao: Niu Piao

269
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:12,200
Tang Lili: Yang Xinnian

270
00:15:12,200 --> 00:15:12,520
Xiao Xingxing: Bao Chenyu

271
00:15:12,520 --> 00:15:13,480
Servant: Zhang Zhiying

272
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:14,440
Bodyguard B: Chen Chuanwei

273
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:14,800
Lu Family Butler: Liu Xin

